reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great product, would buy again!
reviews.reviewText: Love this mirror! Texas heat made my old one melt off so I had to replace. This was the best choice by far. I can see all my blind spots and backing in is a breeze. Super easy and quick install. So far I’ve had it on (through 100+ temps) for a few weeks and it hasn’t budged. I was in a rush so I just used the suction cup bit, no adhesive and it’s doing great. Very sturdy. I will say that when you adjust it, it’s kinda wobbly. Not bad, but it’s got that loose ‘about to fall’ feeling. Again; it hasn’t fallen off so we’re golden. Can’t go wrong with this one.
